name: Dystopian Hours I- Death
description: Welcome to Dystopian Hours, a universe composed of Aldo Rossi buildings, in which you confront your deepest fears and it’s up to you to make it out alive. Cimitero di San Cataldo is the perfect gate to this dark world, where you’re forced to look closely into your soul, to acknowledge your fears and fight back. It’s meant to lure you in, to break you down but also to give you a slight glimmer of hope that there is a light at the end of the tunnel, only if you’re determined to survive. Death, Loneliness, Heartbreak and Failure are my deepest fears. What are you afraid of?
